OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank of England wasn't     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbriefed on mini-budget     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government did not tell the Bank of
OL,6, England about its tax cut plans before 
OL,7, the mini-budget, one of its deputy     
OL,8, governors has said.                    
OL,10,FIn the event, the mini-budget sparked  
OL,11,Fmarket turmoil, with the Bank having to
OL,12,Fstep in to stabilise pension funds.    
OL,14,FThe Bank could have advised the        
OL,15,Fgovernment on the possible market      
OL,16,Freaction, Sir Jon Cunliffe said.       
OL,18,FThe government was criticised for      
OL,19,Fbypassing some independent scrutiny of 
OL,20,Fits plans before making them public.   
